    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "むふふふふ、まだトレンド上位爆走中！\n明日のネットニュースも独占じゃん、これ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mwahahaha‚ we're still trending high!\nWe'll dominate the internet news tomorrow‚ too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.988800303,
      "endTime": 30.9171901384,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 796.5258235999997
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.1221336364
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ。SNSにも写真上げておきなさいよ\n今が一番、注目されてる時間でしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. Post some photos on social media.\nNow's the time when we're getting the most attention‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.1221336364,
      "endTime": 38.076510143300005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.2691180864
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "はっ、そうだった！　山田さんに言われるとか屈辱！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ right! It's humiliating to be reminded by Yamada-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.2691180864,
      "endTime": 42.8781204858,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.0691180864
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "はいはい。ほら、mihoもこっち来て\n営業用の写真だからね、ちゃんとやってよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ yes. Hey‚ miho‚ come over here.\nThis is for promotional photos‚ so do it right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.0691180864,
      "endTime": 51.7101386705,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
