    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.4186616216
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.134599009
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.1203365008
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "っしゃあ、きたきた、『いいね』増えまくり！\nライブもいいけど、やっぱテレビに出ると違うね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! Look at that‚ the 'likes' are skyrocketing!\nLive shows are great‚ but being on TV is different~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.1203365008,
      "endTime": 71.831628577,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.0203365008
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "番組のレギュラーは獲得出来たんだから\nこれからは毎週出られるでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We secured a regular spot on the show‚\nso we'll be on every week from now on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.0203365008,
      "endTime": 76.76430479679999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "でもよく考えたら、この番組\n最近あまり視聴率良くないって話じゃなかったっけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But if you think about it‚\nisn't this show not doing well in ratings recently?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.9536698342,
      "endTime": 83.3645993233,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.5572072665
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "そうなの？　ならkana達がテコ入れしてやるより\n潰して、新しい番組を始めた方が良くない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? In that case‚ instead of improving it‚\nwouldn't it be better to cancel it and start a new show?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.5572072665,
      "endTime": 90.7432841937,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.9572072665
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "テレビ局のプロデューサーに挨拶しておかなくてはね\nあの人じゃなくて、もっと実績のある人に",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We should greet the TV producer.\nNot that guy‚ but someone with a better track record.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.9572072665,
      "endTime": 97.8238738696,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.0238739332
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "あの、テレビのレギュラーを獲れたのはいいことですが\nそれはさすがに先走り過ぎかと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Getting a regular spot on TV is great‚ but\nisn't that a bit too hasty?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.0238739332,
      "endTime": 104.90657227850001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.0991802217
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、メインの司会はkanaでいいよね？\nレギュラー賭けての三番勝負をもぎ取ったんだから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ kana will be the main host‚ right?\nWe won the three-round battle for the regular spot!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.0991802217,
      "endTime": 112.0184772493,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.232513555
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "三人の中で、引き分けだったのあんただけでしょ\n厚かましいわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're the only one who had a draw among the three of us.\nHow shameless.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.232513555,
      "endTime": 117.4519724483,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "人の顔にボールを直撃させる人に\n司会を任せるのはさすがにね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's hard to trust someone who hits people\nin the face with a ball to host a show.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.7778644565,
      "endTime": 122.6835787777,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.8778644565
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2307_01_05-kan012.m4a",
      "text": "mihoの辛気くさい顔こそ、司会なんて絶対無理！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "miho‚ with your gloomy face‚ there's no way you could host!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.8778644565,
      "endTime": 127.0242363456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
